nodes.text: Shippu was a Human female Jedi Master serving the Jedi Order and the  Galactic Republic. During the Cold War she was stationed on Balmorra.
Shippu was originally set to appear in the  video game Star Wars: The Old Republic but for whatever reason her character was cut before release. Shippu's file can be found on Jedipedia.
